Here is the tollfree hotline for the Epilepsy Foundatioof America - 1-800-EFA-1000.  They will be able to answeyour questions and send you information and references oseizure types, medication, etc.  They can also give you referencefor a pediatric neorologist in your area.  Also ask for thenumber of your local Foundation who can put you in touch wita Parent Support Group and social workersGood Luck